snippet.title: Drone Boomerang Shot in Raleigh NC (Peter McKinnon Inspired!)
snippet.description:
Here's my drone boomerang shot for my humble abode, in Raleigh NC! I thought it turned out pretty sweet!

The amazing:
Peter McKinnon: https://www.youtube.com/user/petermckinnon24
Kraig Adams: https://www.youtube.com/user/KadamsMedia

That nice beat:
Dyalla - 4th July https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zpQscTUq2Vc

I used a Phantom 4 Pro drone for this flight. This particular shot with the field and arena in the background made a pretty cinematic drone boomerang.

If you want to learn how to make your own drone boomerang, there's a great tutorial by Kraig Adams:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1py42JP118

Hope ya'll had a great 4th of July if you live in the US! I'd like to know where my subscribers are, so comment below if you'd like to share where you're from!

See you in the next video :)
tags: How to make a boomerang with a drone
